02:53:37.667 --> 02:53:38.667
Abandonar navio.

02:53:40.042 --> 02:53:41.332
Abandonar navio!

02:53:47.083 --> 02:53:48.125
Perto de mim.

02:53:59.250 --> 02:54:00.250
Perto de mim.

02:54:02.708 --> 02:54:03.708
Liberado.

02:54:04.875 --> 02:54:05.875
Liberado.

02:54:11.333 --> 02:54:12.333
Aqui.

