02:58:09.667 --> 02:58:10.999
Spider, aqui.

02:58:11.000 --> 02:58:12.291
Jake!

02:58:12.292 --> 02:58:13.333
Spider!

02:58:24.917 --> 02:58:25.957
Jake!

02:58:25.958 --> 02:58:27.041
Spider!

02:58:39.125 --> 02:58:40.291
