03:01:18.000 --> 03:01:19.000
Que droga!

03:01:39.375 --> 03:01:40.375
Jake!

03:01:41.250 --> 03:01:42.042
Jake!

03:01:48.042 --> 03:01:48.917
Filho!

03:01:51.292 --> 03:01:52.167
Spider, não!

03:01:55.417 --> 03:01:56.499
